verbose_text: The g-allele was also associated with increased expression of MRPS30 in the NBCS normal (p = 0.002, p corrected = 0.36) and breast tumors (p = 0.049, p corrected = 0.43), in GTEx normal breast (p corrected = 0.002), and in TCGA (normal breast p = 6.86 x 10 -5, p corrected = 5.31 x 10 -3 and breast tumors p = 7.21 x 10 -6, p corrected = 9.35 x 10 -4; XREF_FIG B, XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY A, and S1C).
